{"id":103,"count":3,"description":"Unveil the colorful spirit of Gujarat, a land where history, culture, and natural wonders come together. Walk through the white desert of the Rann of Kutch, glowing under the full moon, and experience the vibrant Rann Utsav. Discover the grandeur of Gir National Park, the only home of the Asiatic lions. Admire the exquisite architecture of Somnath and Dwarka temples, and marvel at the stepwells of Patan and Sun Temple at Modhera. Explore the bustling city of Ahmedabad, a UNESCO World Heritage City, with its heritage walks, Sabarmati Ashram, and colorful markets. From the hill temples of Palitana to the serene beaches of Diu, Gujarat offers an unforgettable mix of heritage, spirituality, wildlife, and cultural festivities.","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/destinations\/explore-gujarat\/","name":"EXPLORE GUJARAT","slug":"explore-gujarat","taxonomy":"destination","parent":0,"meta":[],"thumbnail":{"width":900,"height":596,"file":"2025\/09\/EXPLORE-GUJARAT.png","filesize":1045645,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"EXPLORE-GUJARAT-300x199.png","width":300,"height":199,"filesize":41485,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/EXPLORE-GUJARAT-300x199.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"EXPLORE-GUJARAT-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":44442,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/EXPLORE-GUJARAT-150x150.png"},"medium_large":{"file":"EXPLORE-GUJARAT-768x509.png","width":768,"height":509,"filesize":575850,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/EXPLORE-GUJARAT-768x509.png"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"EXPLORE-GUJARAT-374x226.png","width":374,"height":226,"filesize":140959,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/EXPLORE-GUJARAT-374x226.png"},"destination-thumb-size"